Changes to Clock
================

1.5.1
-----
Conversion to new options system, switched to Pango fonts.
New option to not show clock face (requested by Klaus Umbach).

1.5.0
-----
New version for GTK+ 2.0 and ROX-CLib 1.1.0

1.4.1
-----
Fix for being installed in paths with spaces in.

1.4.0
-----
Stable version (unchanged from 1.3.3).

1.3.3
-----
Fix compilation with libxml2.

1.3.2
-----
Use replacement applet menu positioning code (from ROX-CLib).

1.3.1
-----
Another attempt at fixing the bug when time zone changes.c

1.3.0
-----
Multiple windows.  Acts as a server, using SOAP, so there only needs to be
one instance running.

1.2.1
-----
Make sure AppRun can find rox_run.

1.2.0
-----
Minor fixes.

1.1.8
-----
Fix compilation problems.

1.1.7
-----
Use new applet menu positioning code.

1.1.6
-----
Use font selection dialog instead of widget.
Added a monday-thursday repeat.
Test for altzone in <time.h>

1.1.5
-----
Change to XML handling: requires 2.4 or later.  Use old style config otherwise.

1.1.4
-----
Fix memory leak in XML routines.

1.1.3
-----
Can set font for the hour numbers.
Can use a tiled background if you set up your gtkrc.
Fixed bug in new XML format (interval was incorrect)

1.1.2
-----
Configuration and alarms now saved in XML format, old format still supported
when reading.

1.1.1
-----
Small changes to compilation system.

1.1.0
-----
Switch to using ROX-CLib.

1.0.0
-----
No changes.  This is the stable version.

0.1.15
------
Fixed bug in memory management.

0.1.14
------
Support menu accelerators.  Fix bugs in merging alarm files.

0.1.13
------
Drop old (0.1.6) config sypport.  Save alarms file after one is raised.

0.1.12
------
Can configure the initial size

0.1.11
------
Fixed bug in repeating alarms.

0.1.10
------
Fixed bug concealing text label.  Fixed bug in update code.
Some clock face display tweaks.

0.1.9
-----
Added repeating alarms.
Can have the menu on the applet version.

0.1.8
-----
Rudimentary alarm facility.

0.1.7
-----
Support new AppInfo.xml data, debug output off by default.

0.1.6
-----
Re-organised the configuration of the app.  Some tweaks to the display.

0.1.5
-----
Added some locale handling.

0.1.4
-----
More display styles, including a user defined one.

0.1.3
-----
Added different display styles, and a configuration window to choose one.

0.1.2
-----
Corrected hour hand.

0.1.1
-----
Added info window
